Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.22,0:01:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大阪的下町\N阿倍野桥商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.42,0:01:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此处的商店街被建造完成后\N似乎已历经五十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.89,0:01:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到目前为止还没听过\N任何奇怪的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.89,0:01:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,据设计人所说\N这是个历史悠久的商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.13,0:01:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以绝对不会有什么鬼怪啦…\N大魔王啦…巨大机器人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.24,0:01:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与自己相似的家人…\N甚至是性感的波霸姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是完全没有脉络可循
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…那么到底是怎么一回事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.88,0:02:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么说来…设计商店街的那个人\N似乎正从某处注视着他们…呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.43,0:02:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里好像并非原来的商店街\N我和你也完全变了个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.10,0:02:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夜雾让我变得成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.68,0:02:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人真的是太悲哀了，宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨希，打算走了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕竟，我们只是候鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.85,0:02:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,候鸟的命运\N是无法停留在同一个城市的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.59,0:02:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.89,0:02:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里简直就像是个犯罪城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.46,0:02:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连这么可爱的小狗\N影子都是黑漆漆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小狗狗小狗狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.44,0:03:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小步，快逃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好险好险！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.52,0:03:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…那不就是小步的妈妈吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！你好，令堂好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.83,0:03:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里不是说话的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是你被逮捕的话\N鹈鹅家族的脸可就丢大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！你搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.51,0:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鹈鹅的家族是小步\N我们家是乌龟才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.35,0:03:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,废话少说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，被逃走了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.25,0:03:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问，刚刚那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.75,0:03:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鹈鹅家族\N是在此商店街为恶的暴力集团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴力集团？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦…我们的店也开始\N扩充各种买卖了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然会遭遇埋伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第6话 夜雾！\N阿倍野桥☆冷酷无情商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不像你的作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.67,0:04:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是有要紧事要告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.61,0:04:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于传说中的狙击手洛克洛克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要耍小鬼的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.89,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系，那傢伙若是真正的\N职业狙击手，一定会来这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.43,0:04:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小子们，你们绝对要学习\N洛克洛克的工作态度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位客人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我看不见你的脸\N但你是第一次光临敝店吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.64,0:04:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？是…是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你是萨斯派来的奸细？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是间谍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个男的是…\N我们所盼望已久的洛克洛克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.21,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您来的正是时候，客人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…这…怎么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.48,0:05:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.85,0:05:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓的狙击手\N是在不知不觉中出现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那正是那个传说中的男子\N成为传说的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.06,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你从那么远的地方前来\N真是我的荣耀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（阿倍野警察署）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.14,0:05:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请…请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.80,0:05:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是…什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.57,0:05:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小步警官，请注意你的措辞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警官…什么呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.08,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为你介绍你的拍档！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不听人家的话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿倍野天使…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别做蠢事了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有点粗暴\N但还算是个元气十足的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气势也很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.78,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿倍野天使现在要去执行任务了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.84,0:06:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，那是个危险任务\N请务必小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…你们等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问要去哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是已经决定的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,检举鹈鹅家族的暴行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们仍然从事着可恶之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.43,0:06:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是可怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.66,0:06:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓可怕的事是指什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.87,0:06:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，应该让你事先了解才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，无论如何要告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，你是应该先知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.55,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请告诉我，我很在意！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.92,0:07:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,末端价格是一碟三个900元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乞丐蜗牛（奶焗蜗牛）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.42,0:07:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,付土司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是洛克洛克\N知道的很清楚嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这没什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.59,0:07:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我们的资金来源…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.36,0:07:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜禁蜗牛法之赐\N价值才能迅速飙升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此地真的很难做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此传说中的狙击手洛克洛克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.77,0:07:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们需要你上场…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.28,0:07:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标是这个傢伙\N阿倍野桥警察署长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.31,0:07:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.38,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爷爷与我的感情很好的\N所以我来拜托他高抬贵手就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.16,0:07:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎能让传说中的狙击手\N耍那种小鬼头的计谋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛，不然写信也可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.10,0:07:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.96,0:07:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狙击手用的手段\N当然是以枪狙击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用…枪…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以那样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么不可以的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.91,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀人是不可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁说要杀人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说的那么可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管是用枪或什么射击\N人都必死无疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.48,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解了，【法】老大\N我接受这艰难任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的狙击手是最不醒目的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实是很醒目的吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.40,0:08:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,NoNoNo，你这个冒牌货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说他是假冒的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.14,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我才是狙击手洛克洛克\N货真价实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这傢伙居然敢骗我们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.68,0:08:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哪有…是你们自己那样想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，对了这傢伙绝对是假冒的\N没错，很诡异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.89,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狙击手怎会拿着M16A来福枪呢？\N看了就觉得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.99,0:08:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯母，仔细听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.89,0:08:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,此枪的口径是0.223英寸\N发射的子弹属轻量弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子弹初速能高达1000公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但实际的射程只有400公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.17,0:09:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用此种武器狙击\N称得上是职业级的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要对你另眼相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，职业狙击手\N不应受限于武器的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.12,0:09:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此，职业狙击手\N的确要具备此技巧才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.22,0:09:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是觉得这枪很帅\N爱死它了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底谁才是真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等！谁是真的马上就能知晓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.34,0:09:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由你开始\N用那把枪射击那个罐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.71,0:09:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Magnum制的左轮手枪M2006M
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾经很狂热…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伯母，仔细听好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.55,0:09:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只枪呢，只要拆下这个枪管\N便能相互交换
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.45,0:09:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且藉由撞针\N撞击位于圆筒下的子弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.59,0:10:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能大幅减少击发时的后座力\N是此枪的特徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确是如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.87,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少废话，快射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了太棒了\N我射中了！射中了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漂亮！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样也算吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.71,0:10:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游戏规则就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着，轮到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.35,0:10:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来好像是我赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太完美了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.31,0:10:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么蠢话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.05,0:10:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管对手只是一个空罐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.05,0:10:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也毫不留情地催毁至体无完肤\N才具备职业狙击手的特质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.35,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他才是真正传说中的狙击手\N洛克洛克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冒牌者没有用处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎会这样，我什么都没做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的被射中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.14,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,缩小了，好丑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,问题是不知道他们老大\N躲在建筑物中的哪一层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.49,0:11:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正头目是爷爷扮演的\N他不会对我们不利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.43,0:11:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太幼稚了\N大头目是此城市最大的恶党
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来如此\N此城市的恶党正暗自地谋取暴利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.78,0:11:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若想让城市真的和平\N就应该设法拔掉此毒瘤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了，这样的穿着太过显目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的太显目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.35,0:12:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太醒目\N那为什么要以这种打扮外出呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.45,0:12:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,木奈木奈警官\N为此早准备好潜入用的服装了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.09,0:12:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.89,0:12:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们真是太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.49,0:12:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然一开始便已想到会如此\N为何不一开始就那样穿呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.30,0:12:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是沙也香警官\N迅速展开作战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不听人家说的话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.64,0:12:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？什么！难不成要我在这里换装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！快住手！就算是小学生\N也不能在这种地方换装吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都往这边看了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.18,0:12:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！你们！等一下\N色鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.55,0:12:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂！你们别不理我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可怜的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.29,0:12:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成那副可笑的样子\N你已无翻身之地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此商店街中\N再也不会有人理你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永远都不会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说谁的样子可笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.34,0:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只不过是…缩小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.67,0:13:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个洛克洛克更好笑\N为了一个啤酒罐用炸药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.69,0:13:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚还有歌曲表演吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.36,0:13:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唱歌…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会唱歌吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.10,0:13:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是你召我的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美…美毙了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好逊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.73,0:14:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成那么成熟妩媚的小步\N是不会再理我这种丑角了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是看开点看开点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个男的不是老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定躲在更隐密的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.91,0:14:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二楼的房间全都查过了\N剩下的就只有这上面…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,~超级角色登场~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.47,0:14:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…没射中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.17,0:14:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼哼哼…\N这就是我传说中所谓的神话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在要给你们致命一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛克洛克被击中了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,缩小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.92,0:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察！全部逮捕！\N给我老实点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要谁老实？…你在跟谁说教啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.63,0:15:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里由我负责，去抓老大！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了！拜托！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.54,0:15:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，萨希！跑哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.12,0:15:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于找到了…手举起来\N大头目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.63,0:15:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是一样地粗暴呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说过没上锁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.97,0:15:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要逮捕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逮捕后要做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么消失的无影无踪呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直都在等待着你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.91,0:15:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在等，一直在等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.28,0:15:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经是过去的事了\N无法再重新来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.92,0:15:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像此恒星的运转一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.09,0:16:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类的命运从未偏离过此轨道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你所谓的全部啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所说的全部是宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.30,0:16:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我的心就像在此地狱中一样\N在空虚的城市苦苦地守候着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,且要永远地彷徨流连下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.34,0:16:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你认为这只是命运的极少部份\N可以一起背负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.75,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光是背负着自己的使命\N就已精疲力尽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.75,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.78,0:16:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到下面去抓雅之吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.99,0:16:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的目标是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，请不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安倍先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,缩小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.11,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成丑角觉得很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.05,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.72,0:17:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事\N为什么会变成此模样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.85,0:17:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼，大人有太多事需要去做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管耍酷还是一样让人觉得滑稽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少管我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问，哪里能找到萨希？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.74,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在没心情管那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.41,0:17:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天明明有个\N绝佳机会观测天文的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.81,0:17:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教雅之卖蜗牛真是太不智了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.18,0:17:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里太过严肃了\N我要搬到稍微轻松的世界去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等…等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.15,0:17:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要一个，只要一个愿望\N我想回到原本的世界中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.99,0:17:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不是请求小鬼\N带你们回去的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小鬼太不可靠了\N一点也不值得信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是错误百出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.67,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次总是想要回家的\N但却老是被送到奇怪之处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.80,0:17:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被送到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.91,0:18:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且都是这些非常奇怪的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既是如此的话希望之神\N应该正确地被召唤才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.05,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界之所以不一样\N尽管多少会偏离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不致于会造成这样的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.35,0:18:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为鬼若失手的话\N你们应该会留在原来的世界才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那为什么我们回不了家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你们不想回去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能！我明明…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知怎么搞的\N他与我有着难解的缘份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时甚至会造成我的困扰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变得这么丑的萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.85,0:18:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的确\N他与你有着难解的缘份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.82,0:18:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝不再让你们在此时空中\N到处乱窜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快给我回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我来送你们一程吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.79,0:18:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使是皇帝也不会如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大臣的话绝对不会那么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔为何那么生气呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.80,0:19:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脚变得那么短\N心情肯定是不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.11,0:19:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了哦\N接着知道该怎么做了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.92,0:19:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.98,0:19:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…没什么…\N回家吧，回我们的阿倍野桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.26,0:19:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.96,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.89,0:19:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不觉得有点遗憾吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.63,0:19:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.10,0:19:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,与其回到原来的城市\N不如在不同世界中穿梭来的快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.21,0:19:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不觉得吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.04,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，事实上我也是那么觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想想不管到何处\N都能得到最喜欢的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.98,0:19:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此在念诵回家的咒文时\N不…一想到接着不知会发生何事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.82,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,内心便会变得非常的兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.33,0:20:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.13,0:20:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.96,0:20:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先前我还感到有点莫名其妙\N怎么想都想不出个所以然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在我终于知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.98,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是因为你这个笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.31,0:20:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次会穿梭在这么奇怪的世界\N全是因为你的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不是点头佩服的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不都是因为你\N才让我感到疲劳不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.02,0:20:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.19,0:20:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一回到原来的阿倍野桥的话\N小步就要搬走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.86,0:20:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又如何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.10,0:20:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就见不到面了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.23,0:20:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛，那也是没办法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是没办法…\N但那样就看不到小步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.07,0:20:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然会有点寂寞…\N但已是无法挽回的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.94,0:20:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.21,0:20:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇敢面对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.28,0:20:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨希若永远处于这样的世界中\N那又会如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.68,0:21:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种搞不清明天昨天的世界里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.72,0:21:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又有什么关系…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.36,0:21:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话其实也没什么不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现实一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直待在这样的地方\N什么都不能做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.73,0:21:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该检讨反省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.27,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想回到\N平常大家居住的世界里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.61,0:21:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且也希望能考虑到家人朋友\N还有萨希的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们回去吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.98,0:21:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了…小步果然很伟大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.42,0:21:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次我会好好想着回去之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.92,0:21:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在这世上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.97,0:21:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有天尊神明与地尊神明啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在这世上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.54,0:21:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有天尊神明与地尊神明啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在这世上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.88,0:22:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有天尊神明与地尊神明啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,急急如律令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回的阿倍野桥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.82,0:23:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别再胡闹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.12,0:23:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次来到这胡扯的世界\N全是因为你的缘故…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佩服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.29,0:23:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么好佩服的\N别再乱搞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.72,0:23:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暂停一下，先谈谈下回…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.46,0:23:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，我绝不容许再有下回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.46,0:23:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话虽如此\N但那是我特地为你而做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不需要特地那么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.23,0:24:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么幼稚的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.23,0:24:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幼稚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.14,0:24:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了，先谈谈下回预告…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.74,0:24:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，不好意思\N这次不能让你做预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.61,0:24:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我要\N下回的阿倍野桥商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.37,0:24:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇…哇…哇…
